===Noun phrase===
'''[[plasma]] [[accelerator]]''' (''plural'' '''plasma accelerators''')
#{{physics}} A [[particle accelerator]] that uses [[plasma]] as the medium of the accelerating field instead of a vacuum, to obtain a larger accelerating gradient.

